this_title: Amy Winehouse: I Told You I Was Trouble
introduction: I Told You I Was Trouble: Live In London is a music DVD and Blu-ray disc of contemporary R&B singer Amy Winehouse, recorded at London's Shepherds Bush Empire in London, England. The DVD was released on 5 November 2007.Track listingLive in London title:Intro/"Addicted""Just Friends""Cherry""Back To Black""Wake Up Alone""Tears Dry On Their Own""He Can Only Hold Her""Doo Wop (That Thing)" (Lauryn Hill cover)"Fuck Me Pumps""Some Unholy War""Love Is A Losing Game""Valerie""Hey Little Rich Girl" feat.
